                                <div>
                                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2">Enterprise-Grade Security</h5>
                                    <p class="mb-0">We implement industry-standard security measures including data encryption, secure authentication, and regular security audits to protect your personal and financial information.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row g-3 mt-3">
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <i class="fas fa-key fa-3x text-primary mb-2"></i>
                                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Encrypted Storage</h6>
                                    <small class="text-muted">All data encrypted at rest</small>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <i class="fas fa-user-lock fa-3x text-success mb-2"></i>
