                                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">You can modify your personal information anytime through your account settings.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <div class="right-card p-3 border rounded">
                                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2">
                                        <i class="fas fa-trash text-warning me-2"></i>Delete Account
